{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1473626, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《三体》", "timestamp": 1618668865, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "初一初二水平已经完全不影响网上冲浪了\n科幻小说生词会更多吧", "timestamp": 1618668877, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473630, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体", "timestamp": 1618668885, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473633, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体？", "timestamp": 1618668909, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473635, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体！", "timestamp": 1618668913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473636, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体...？就是可能会涉及到一些比较复杂的名词", "timestamp": 1618668914, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473638, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大刘的短篇", "timestamp": 1618668928, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "别看长的，可能看不下去", "timestamp": 1618668940, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473641, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "故事会咋子也不错", "timestamp": 1618668951, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473644, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "杂志", "timestamp": 1618668961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "球形闪电", "timestamp": 1618668970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "国外作品的译作也可以吧，要是dz喜欢魔戒、冰火之类的直接读中文版就好了，熟悉情节的话也便于理解", "timestamp": 1618668974, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473648, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从《三体》开始看吧，cz喜欢的还有《呼吸》《降临》（特德姜的短篇小说集），《与拉玛相会》《神们自己》《永恒的终结》等等也挺好的。如果喜欢科幻奇幻类可以来科幻协会hhh", "timestamp": 1618668980, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473650, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以多和别人聊天联系中文", "timestamp": 1618668992, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "科幻的话三体就行，同样推荐刘慈欣的其他作品。\n可以上喜马拉雅搜主播“大屁股老鼠哈哈笑”讲的很好", "timestamp": 1618668997, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体 yyds", "timestamp": 1618669009, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "讲真看翻译过来的科幻似乎差点味。。。", "timestamp": 1618669031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473670, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还是看儿童文学吧", "timestamp": 1618669118, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实dz也可以试试金庸的武侠小说", "timestamp": 1618669176, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473683, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "玄幻的话试试武侠？（金庸，古龙等等，但是难度会有点大？）", "timestamp": 1618669190, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473686, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "刘慈欣的大部分作品应该都不会用什么难词", "timestamp": 1618669211, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473688, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Nathan: 但会出现长牙的鲸鱼（）", "timestamp": 1618669232, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473691, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体太大部头了，先看点中短篇吧\n推荐《带上她的眼睛》《地球大炮》《欢乐颂》《微纪元》《超新星纪元》", "timestamp": 1618669267, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473728, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《冰与火之歌》，如果看过原版就更好了", "timestamp": 1618669785, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473736, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好家伙，这里就是我大刘安利楼呗", "timestamp": 1618669846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473754, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "乡村教师也可", "timestamp": 1618669955, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1473757, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Queen", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你用母语看过的文学作品呀～我就是这么学外语的，每学一门外语就看那种语言的《哈利波特》😆", "timestamp": 1618669991, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474154, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Richard", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我再说一个方法吧，你可以看看国内学生的初高中语文课本，还可以顺便学习古文哦～", "timestamp": 1618673192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474174, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Susan", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 草，这是哪位朋友", "timestamp": 1618673384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474264, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Thomas", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "幻想小说的话，可以试试江南的九州缥缈录\n另外或许可以试试初中推荐的一些必读书目，可能主题的深度不深，但是语言比较容易懂。\n如果对偏向古文的小说感兴趣，可以试试水浒传。\n可能红楼梦、西游记等书籍并不仅仅是语言上的难度，也有可能是文化差异导致的理解困难。对于土生土长的中国同学而言，一些东西是熟视无睹的，但是对于国际同学而言，这些东西如果不做出提前说明，是很难理解的。", "timestamp": 1618674192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1474944, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Uma", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么没人推荐儿童读物呢🧐城南旧事 草房子 我觉得都不错", "timestamp": 1618679963, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1475683, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Vivian", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "斗破苍穹", "timestamp": 1618709946, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1475955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Winnie", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "起点中文网上的奇幻都挺好的，按排行榜搜一下", "timestamp": 1618713598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1476636, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Xander", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "余华可以试着接触\n冯骥才有一本俗世奇人 都是小短篇 我初中看的 也挺有意思并且语言很通俗生动\n之前高中语文阅读题做到过刘震云好像也还行？\n不过感觉围城不是很难懂啊..cz超级喜欢的）", "timestamp": 1618720591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1476654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Thomas", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Uma: 我也觉得草房子挺适合的", "timestamp": 1618720789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1477106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Yasmine", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "临高启明（逃）", "timestamp": 1618726167, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1477132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Zach", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《射雕英雄传》、《天龙八部》、《倚天屠龙记》等。", "timestamp": 1618726549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1477162, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Alice", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哈利波特系列（？当时学英语的时候也读了英文版", "timestamp": 1618727171, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1478871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Susan: 是某幽灵会员hhh", "timestamp": 1618744570, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1479957, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Bob", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "临高启明", "timestamp": 1618753223, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1479995, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Carol", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三体或者哈利波特", "timestamp": 1618753518, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1480319, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Dave", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "试试自己母语作品的中文译作，原文译文对比看...？", "timestamp": 1618756300, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1480389, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哇！有很多推荐，谢谢大家 - ̗̀(๑ᵔ⌔ᵔ๑)", "timestamp": 1618756735, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1481014, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Angry Eve", "pid": 289126, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "汪曾祺的短篇也可以试试", "timestamp": 1618832631, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 25, "pid": 289126, "reply": 44, "tag": null, "text": "#小说推荐\n\n大家好，我是个国际生，估计我的汉语水平是初一初二的。有时学汉语是一个很无聊的现象；死记硬背单词、分析语病、刷题等等都让我头疼，但是我真的希望能够提高我的汉语能力。我认为看小说是一个很好的帮助，但是现在我只看漫画或网络小说。我想开始看纸质版的小说，可是《红楼梦》、《围城》、《西游记》的文学不太适合我。有没有科幻、奇幻之类的小说能推荐给我吗？\n\n谢谢- ̗̀(๑ᵔ⌔ᵔ๑)", "timestamp": 1618668798, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618832631, "url": "", "vote": {}}}